data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 2-story property has it all. With 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a 3-car garage, there's plenty of space for everyone. The office space and formal dining area provide the perfect balance of work and entertainment. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious loft that can be used as a game room, and a separate media room for movie nights. The breakfast area and butler's pantry are perfect for hosting gatherings. Cozy up by the fireplace or step out onto the balcony for some fresh air. The great size covered porch-patio is perfect for outdoor relaxation. The vaulted ceilings and walk-in closets add a touch of luxury. Minute walk from splash pad and community playground.City sports complex 5 minute drive from location.  Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to call this house your home!
